synthesis_method: The electrolyte synthesis process involves mixing lithium acetate dihydrate, manganese acetate tetrahydrate, and tetramethoxysilane, grinding the mixture with zirconia pellets for 60 hours, drying, powdering, heat treating at 350°C, and further treating at 800°C in a reducing air stream to yield 13 g of Li2MnSiO4 with an 81% yield.
